snippet.title: Demonstar Secret Missions 1 Full Game Playthrough [PC]
snippet.description:
Full game gameplay of Demonstar : Secret Missions 1

About This Game : 
This is a spinoff title from the original DemonStar game, which uses an enhanced version of the original engine.

Story : 
The enemy alien race, the Xidus were busy developing in secret new, more powerful DemonStar ships to destroy Earth. As usual, the player's mission is to battle his way through hordes of new enemies, and destroy their devastating new weapons.

If you like this video consider clicking that like button, subscribe for more and hit the notification to get notified when new video drops
Thank You.
